Package: gazeneuro
Title: Gaze Tracking and Neuroimaging Integration
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Prince", "Eric", , "Eric.Prince@CUAnschutz.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7359-6608"))
Description: Provides tools for integrating eye tracking gaze data with NIfTI 
    neuroimaging files. Includes functions for temporal alignment, coordinate 
    transformation, and visualization of gaze patterns on brain slices.
